data.description: **RECENTLY REDUCED** UNRESTRICTED property with spacious yard! Many new recent upgrades, MUST SEE! Schedule your showing today! Beautiful entrance with wrought iron fence with 2 large gates for easy access for trucks, tractors, boats or cars. Extra building on the property can be used as a workshop w/ 3 garage bays or can even be used as office space or living quarters as this space includes a restroom and electricity. The home has 4 bedrooms. Primary bedroom with his & her separate bathrooms and closets, 3 upstairs- one to be used for a study, sitting area or bedroom. Designed with 5 Bay Windows, formal living & dining, family room with a stone fireplace, kitchen has walk-in-pantry with bar area for barstools facing the kitchen, spacious laundry & storage rooms. Very private and well maintained. Excellent for Residential or Commercial use. A great place to enjoy the end of the day. Come have a look!
